      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents the pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single scratch, dent, or stone chip to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery and trim showing absolutely no signs of wear, still carrying that new-car feel. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously serviced on schedule with a full history available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
