    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved over the years. Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
