    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically sound, it has received critical preventative maintenance including VANOS adjustment and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings, while the factory M-variable limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery through the corners. The individual throttle bodies provide razor-sharp response, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A robust specimen that balances mechanical purity with visceral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
