    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure valvetrain precision. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a well-maintained suspension setup that preserves the car's legendary handling characteristics. While showing signs of careful use, the powertrain remains in excellent health, offering the tactile, analog driving experience this platform is renowned for.",
